latestPosts.caption:
MAGICMAN 2 is out
There you go.. 
I want to share to everyone 
What i experienced
How i honestly feel
Sharing to my community what I want to say as a person
And Lastly, How I recovered from everything

I have decided to step away from everything last year mainly because i couldn’t answer the question
“Am i the jackson that everyone know of or am i the jackson i know”
The sad thing was I couldn’t even answer who i am

I took the year off
Thinking and processing my entire life
Spending quality time with my family
Writing personal journals
Rearranging plans
Reflecting on what everything mean to me
Admitting the mistakes I have caused
Being patient to listen to my heart
What really healed and helped me recover was giving time and love to connect with myself
The self that I have been escaping from for a very long time

It was very important for me to take that time off and put myself together
Mentally and physically

I arranged the album in 4 chapters
From
Chapter 1: Manic highs
Chapter 2: Loosing control
Chapter 3: Realization
Chapter 4: Acceptance
Which I have concluded that’s literally like every situation in life

In life
We always run into chaotic situations
Then we react emotionally
Then we realize a lot of things that’s hard to accept
At the end of the day
What has been done, cant be undone
We always accept it and move on with a better understanding of life

I have mentioned this a lot of times,
“Everyone needs their own version of MAGICMAN to grow”
What I am really saying is :
“Everyone needs to give enough time, effort and love to your inner self in order to grow and evolve the way we truly want”

I wouldn’t have recovered from it if I didn’t do so

The good & the bad in life
It’s all meant to happen
And it made who you are today

live the magic, everyone.
live the magic, Jackson.
.
Thank you for the ones that have been with me for so long
Im sure some of you also grew up together with me
Thank you for giving me the opportunity to appear in your life
I hope this album can also give you energy and motivation to heal yourself as well
I care and I love you a lot

- jackson
